nodes.text: Dwoogan was a female chef aboard the Wayward Current. Before she was a chef, she was a pilot for the Galactic Republic.

Dwoogan was a pilot in the Galactic Republic. She once went to the Dande Donjon, a cantina on the Shore of Vette Lake at Xu'hu, where she met Redy, who told her a conspiracy theory against the Alliance to Restore the Republic.
In her later life she became a chef aboard the Wayward Current she once told a story to the crew members of the Wayward Current about a conspiracy theory that Redy told her in the Dande Donjon.
Dwoogan was a tall, muscular woman with scars on her face. She was known on the Wayward Current as a someone who could turn the most revolting ingredients into something delicious.
